page.title: 02ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS.
page.content:
The information on this block of land was compiled, edited and typed by 11 3rd and 4th year children from Winhills County Junior School, St. Neots. Their contributions are as follows.
Page 1 - Anthony Thompson & Steven Gould. Pages 3&4 - Sarah Anderson. Pages 5 to 10(incl.) - Emma Hammond. Page 11. - Daniel Light. Pages 12 to 15(incl.) - Tracey Oddy. Page 16 - Diane Rudd. Page 17 - Donna Wrench. Page 18 - Jeremy Young. Page 19 - Tammy Keeble. Page 20 - Nicola Fox.
The project and subsequent work was supervised by Juliana Dickinson, Gareth Stealey and David Price; all of whom teach at the School. Photographs, all taken in 1985, are from the school's own archives.
